{"tid":1246264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"送禮比警犬","createTime":"2019-06-20T15:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T16:48:28.000Z","uid":214984,"like":8,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3604e6e8f2465d2e4a308c654729c01df13dba45","tid":1246264,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"隔離po屌緊啲人送禮向警犬釋出善意<br />\n首先放低對佢哋惡行嘅憎恨，理性少少諗，其實我覺得<span style=\"font-size: large;\">未嘗不可！</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 不割蓆不分化，各有各做<br />\n2. 其實係一種拎道德高地嘅宣傳，想像下上報啲港豬會點睇，又拎分！<br />\n3. 好多人都講緊警察內部士氣好低，我哋咁樣其實係將喺左右邊境嘅佢哋輕輕一拉<br />\n4. 減低對前線傷害作為會衝嘅人，真係見過有推緊線嘅警犬比理性喝一喝會停一停<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">喺警察內部人心都好動搖嘅時候，收買人心嘅attempt不失為一個策略</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申發夢，衝時要照衝。都係嗰句，衝一定要有合理目的"},{"pid":"b5a1702f8fe7a362f0b2071f3b467d36ff6e291c","tid":1246264,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a401d77f5066b7945578a3653a594c0cacb417db","tid":1246264,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc62a431e28b313395813c677b4b590eeeff9cd","tid":1246264,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />           <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=